<div class="section_offset">
  <div class="container clearfix">
    <div class="row">
      <section class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 m_xs_bottom_30">
        <h3 class="color_dark fw_light m_bottom_15 heading_1 t_align_c">FAQ</h3>
        <p class="m_bottom_35 heading_2 t_align_c"></p>   
        <div class="tabs t_align_c">
          <div id="tab-1">
            <div class="accordion t_align_l">
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">What is VirtuTV?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">VirtuTV is a decentralized news platform for journalists and content creators. It uses the PNDAs currency, the defacto currency of the VirtuTV Project.</dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">What can you do with VirtuTV?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">Monetize your journalistic content, share it on social media, remain anonymous if desired, compete with other journalists to earn reputation points and earn PNDAs.</dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all"> Will more Pandacoins be sold?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">No. To provide the upmost transparency and stability to the community, only the Pandacoins issued during the crowdsale will be sold. </dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">Is it free to create an account?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">Yes. VirtuTV will never take a fee from its users.</dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">What cryptocoin will I be able to use on VirtuTV?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">For the alpha product, PNDA's will be the currency of the VirtuTV Platform. Once the beta is finished, we will introduce Bitcoin and Ether.</dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">Will I be able to earn money on the platform?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">Yes. All users can earn money by setting pricing and receiving perks for their journalism in the form of PNDA's, which is the currency of the VirtuTV Platform.</dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">How long until rollout after the crowdsale?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">Alpha testing of our platform will begin 4 weeks after the crowdsale for crowdsale participants! You can expect our beta to launch in the Fall of 2017.</dd>
              </dl>
              <dl class="accordion_item r_corners wrapper m_bottom_5 tr_all">
                <dt class="accordion_link relative color_dark tr_all">How do I get an invite to the alpha?
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block hide">
                    <i class="icon-minus"></i>
                  </span>
                  <span class="icon_wrap_size_1 circle d_block show">
                    <i class="icon-plus"></i>
                  </span>
                </dt>
                <dd class="fw_light color_dark">Once you contribute to the crowdsale, you will receive an invite via email to our platform. Continue to check our website and slack/social media channels for announcements.</dd>
              </dl>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
